VZhang, DB (reprint author), Shanghai Jiao Tong Univ, Sch Life Sci & Biotechnol,Shanghai Inst Biol Sci, Minist Educ,Key Lab Microbial Metab, Penn State Univ Joint Ctr Life Sci, Shanghai 200240, Peoples R China.
